description-en_US-print:
ViewSonic’s new 42” (VT4236LED) professional display features full HD 1920x1080p WLED panel technology, professional connectivity and hospitality features. These features combined with its slim design and energy saving electronics makes the VT4236LED an ideal solution for your business and entertainment needs. Additional features include RS232 automated control port, IR pass through, and USB cloning calibration. Additional features include versatile inputs featuring an ATSC (HDTV) TV tuner, 3 HDMI ports, VGA, component video, and USB multimedia input.

<b>Mercury-Free LED Backlight/Energy Saving</b>
Full HD 1920x1080 WLED panel uses less energy than conventional CDFL flat panels while producing richer colors, brighter whites and blacker black.

<b>Advanced Image Processing Delivers Crisp Sharp Images</b>
Advanced ClearPicture image processing eliminates noise, increases contrast and detail while optimizing color for rich, vibrant images.

<b>OptiSync Technology For Extreme Connectivity</b>
Extreme versatility is provided with 3 HDMI, HDCP compliant inputs in addition to RGB PC, component and composite video, ATSC (QAM) TV tuner and a USB port for viewing JPEG images.

Applications:
- Hospitality / Entertainment display;
- Business / Educational display – boardroom and classroom;
- Low cost digital signage - small to mid size business;
- Medical office and waiting room entertainment displays;
- Hotel guest room entertainment;
- Sports bar and restaurant entertainment displays.
